# Public Google OAuth client id for Drive appdata sync.
# Create an OAuth client (type: Web application) in Google Cloud Console with:
#   Dev authorized JavaScript origin:  http://localhost:3000
#   Prod authorized JavaScript origin: https://your-domain.example  (HTTPS required)
# Also enable the Google Drive API in the same GCP project (APIs & Services → Library).
# Then copy this file to .env.local and fill in the value.
# Leaving this empty runs JackPass in local-only mode (no Google Drive sync).
# Rebuild (bun run build) after changing this value — it is baked into the bundle.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
